WEBVTT

00:11.238 --> 00:13.040
Let me go now, please.

00:13.071 --> 00:14.337
Your wife's sick.

00:14.363 --> 00:15.787
What if I could help her?

00:15.867 --> 00:19.982
Khatri found someone with
altered genetic qualities.

00:20.008 --> 00:21.767
A way to repair diseases.

00:21.793 --> 00:22.883
Speak to Khatri.

00:22.909 --> 00:24.721
(SCREAMS)

00:24.747 --> 00:26.291
We need to get you to the hospital.

00:26.317 --> 00:27.513
You need stitches.

00:27.793 --> 00:29.721
Talk to her. Calm her down.

00:29.747 --> 00:30.947
Let me go!

00:30.973 --> 00:32.276
Who's the extraction?

00:32.302 --> 00:33.302
It's the sheriff.

00:33.328 --> 00:34.728
Anything we should know?

00:34.754 --> 00:36.321
Bit of a character apparently.

00:37.105 --> 00:39.137
It's not this boy who'll kill the demon.

00:39.163 --> 00:42.116
It's you. Only Dan.

00:43.446 --> 00:44.750
Too late.

